The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 PM kin arrest

 Ludhiana, June 23 (PTI): The husband and in-laws of Amneet Kaur, a relative of Prime Minister Manmohan Singh, were arrested today for allegedly harassing her for dowry, a senior police official said.

 Amneet, the granddaughter of Singhs sister-in-law, lodged an FIR with Khanna police station, saying she was thrown out of her in-laws house, along with her six-month-old daughter, for not bringing sufficient dowry after her marriage in January 2006.




